{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now that I'm thinking to tell people you will die in three minutes or two minutes or five minutes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you are dead, well you're going to-- you are going to cry no more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are going to [INAUDIBLE] can tell anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the process was, as far as I knew, that it would take from 2 to 5 minutes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After, very seldom you would find somebody that was alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And ?] you never find somebody is alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All these things, the capos are doing most of the things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not getting involved too much in--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were busy doing something-- cleaning, you know, where there's a lot of people over there that left everything there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So some of the food always we took out for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How they-- how they died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tough, tough things.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always the capos were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a-- a very terrific scene.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see all from regular people, you see just coming in a few minutes ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You open the door after 30 minutes, and you see a [INAUDIBLE] 1,500 2,000, 2,500, all dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is always that my mind, because it is a very, very hard view to see people that you saw them before, and all of a sudden you see them 5, 10 minutes late, they are all dead.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you know, with the gas-- with the gas they get blue, and they get, you know, you have to work hard to untie them to be able to drag them out, put them in the thing, to put them in the elevator.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it looks, you know, they are like this, like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always they are bending.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They stay up, you know, when the gas [INAUDIBLE] goes down.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
